{"tid":1359860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請入黎, 要人數取勝, 7月27 元朗遊行, 前哨戰","createTime":"2019-07-24T08:29:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T11:25:36.000Z","uid":22097,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"55acfce8d2113cc0e960306d4a6f6e23a5507d11","tid":1359860,"uid":22097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:29:42.000Z","msg":"1.<br />\n請盡快傳開去 ：<br />\n由於現時警方仍在審核本星期六元朗遊行嘅申請, 警方亦正在收集反對聲音的人數作為是否批核的理據， 如果你哋唔希望元朗成為戰場,&nbsp; 請致電元朗警署 36611680（ 電話已被證實,&nbsp; 只需講出姓名身份證及聯絡號碼就可以<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n大家如果認同為了保障元朗社區安寧，警方應該停止向&ldquo;光復元朗&rdquo;示威者發出&ldquo;遊行不反對通知書&rdquo;，請立即發電郵或傳真予警方。<br />\n電郵: sslo-1-yldist@police.gov.hk<br />\n傳真: 24427301<br />\n<br />\n致:元朗警區指揮官<br />\n本人强烈反對向&ldquo;光復元朗&rdquo;遊行發出&ldquo;不反對通知書&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n簽署:<br />\n2019年7月24日<br />\n<br />\n事緣呢兩個whatsapp 係元朗啲鄉下佬到傳出黎, 跟手跟電話確認元朗警署過去呢幾個鐘全部都係做緊上面嘅野, 瘋狂幫人登記反對批不反對通知書, 雖然警方應該以佢個&quot;專業&quot;決定批定唔批, 但佢地咁做係唔批嘅時候會加大左自己理據<br />\n<br />\n所以如果你喺過去曾經出過黎好，冇出過黎好，都應該係呢個時候做返啲嘢, 簡單打幾個電話/ send email, 支持警方批不反對通知書, 或者係投訴警方遲遲唔發出不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n香港需要你, 如果你地唔做呢步, 警方大可以話無人支持都得, 所以請大家幫幫手"},{"pid":"0b90fe513c86e19f4071fb8819fac31736e8bbe4","tid":1359860,"uid":22097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:31:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0197d7e83cfb7dadc2feaca84815d4da29bd3ee1","tid":1359860,"uid":22097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:33:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c974770342f8860aeb1b56732f5cf8421d95ac87","tid":1359860,"uid":22097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:36:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"728dfb433118da99986f9430938d31f116055dfb","tid":1359860,"uid":51246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:37:13.000Z","msg":"727 po又沉底"},{"pid":"592a48f4b7863b993b9c9d5449f86a1ef0783759","tid":1359860,"uid":22097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:38:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a73b9040b1d704e79b6feddd63d201e03e4e1e5f","tid":1359860,"uid":60615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:38:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"953a6ecac75e5b2d8f19ebd35a52154d08e86803","tid":1359860,"uid":22097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:39:42.000Z","msg":"send 個email, 打幾個電話咋, 唔洗以街, 唔洗出汗, 最輕鬆支持, 不理老幼, 係人就得, 咁都唔做?"},{"pid":"5d9c3fcac9753b4046704ff5a2de20f5e32a2658","tid":1359860,"uid":22097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:41:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc4db1e0c51379860e9c5c8509aef87a05566b1d","tid":1359860,"uid":22097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:44:05.000Z","msg":"我地已經慢左人半日, 仲唔追返個勢? 到時比警隊話, 大部分人都反對遊行, 咁樣真係好咩"},{"pid":"d32e460f9386b35bc6990c405df3aca0145120ba","tid":1359860,"uid":22097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:47:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00d114bbabe5244eaaeabdac5f7a17cea1ce5aa5","tid":1359860,"uid":22097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:47:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c13728421f9504c02817f5241ca00439e6d4ac04","tid":1359860,"uid":22097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:47:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27fff25f102cdb2c69bda288019c12f893adbd82","tid":1359860,"uid":22097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:48:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f04b66d2a5d64159d84aaa5cc7637ded19a14b4a","tid":1359860,"uid":22097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:50:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4df216edd532262e9adaff6046f9a5e2d1aeed07","tid":1359860,"uid":22097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:50:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a26f167e95597e53df1c02b9e5bbc55167732e0","tid":1359860,"uid":22097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:50:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bc783641fb893248e3f37c1b0e206a1755453c0","tid":1359860,"uid":22097,"l